title: Dakine Duster Glove
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2014 Duster Glove in our Union print.
Duster Glove Features:
- Insert: DK Dry waterproof
- Insulation: High loft synthetic insulation [ 80g ]
- Palm: Durable water repellent leather
- Shell: Nylon / Poly with DWR treatment / Durable water repellent suede
- Lining: 230g Fleece / 400g Pile
- Cuff Closure: Zipper
